Madlaine Traverse https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Madlaine_Traverse 0 Madlaine Traverse (born Mary Businsky, August 1, 1875 - January 7, 1964) was an American stage and screen actress from Cleveland, Ohio. In the course of her career she is alternately billed as "Madaline Traverse", "Madeline Traverse" and "Madeline Travers".
